parcel.name: White Cube
parcel.description:
**KILL ME IN THE METAVERSE** is the official virtual launch event for the new single from Daichi Yamamoto and Mick Jenkins, “**Kill Me**” available on all streaming platforms today [here](https://ssm.lnk.to/KillMe "here").  

The event is being produced by newly launched record label and production studio, [Frank Renaissance](https://www.frankrenaissance.com/ "Frank Renaissance") in collaboration with, [Jazzy Sport](https://jazzysport.com/ "Jazzy Sport") and [DAOrecords](https://www.daorecords.org/ "DAOrecords") and will take place on 5/9 10AM JST & 5/8 9PM EST & 8PM CST  in a ethereum-based virtual world called Cryptovoxels, at a venue called “**White Cube**” in the Tokyo neighborhood.

Participants can join as their avatars and will be able to interact with and purchase one of a kind NFTs, view and purchase a limited edition “**Kill Me**” music video and watch a live Q&A session with artists [Mick Jenkins](https://twitter.com/mickjenkins "Mick Jenkins") and [Daichi Yamamoto](https://twitter.com/daichiyamoto "Daichi Yamamoto").
